CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in New Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, November 3, 1973, pg. 1 reads:"Homecoming Queen - Miss Gail Minor, the first Black Homecoming Queen in Pitt history, rides in parade with Chancellor Wesley W. Posvar. (Photo by Teenie Harris)."
TitMainTitle: University of Pittsburgh Chancellor Wesley Posvar seated next to first black Homecoming Queen Gail Minor in back of convertible with "Baierl Chevrolet" sign, in homecoming parade in front of Cathedral of Learning, University of Pittsburgh, Oakland
